ED_Title: Question of the Comorian island of Mayotte
ED_DecisionText: At its 108th plenary meeting, on 6 September 2024, the General Assembly, the General Assembly decided to include the item entitled “Question of the Comorian island of Mayotte” in the draft agenda of its seventy-ninth session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
